Gg_lg_bunker
-------------

This map contains two bunkers that are seperated by a cilinder.
There are 5 possible routes to go trough.
Remember: The enmeny can see your head when you're running trough the side-bunkers on the second floor.
The windows break when they receive 75 damage.

Good luck everyone,
Have fun,

Grtz The Lethal Mapping Team
